      "name": "Cancer Screenings",
      "code": "PX070901",
      "abbreviation": "PX070901",
      "description": "These self-administered questions ask about different cancer screening tests a respondent may have had in the past 3 years. The protocol includes the following screenings: mammogram, pap smear, pelvic examination, Prostate Specific Antigen (PSA) test, colonoscopy, ultrasound of the ovaries, barium e",
